Sopon M(1), Oleksik V(2), Roman M(3), Cofaru N(4), Oleksik M(4), Mohor C(5), 
Boicean A(6), Fleaca R(3).

Author information:
(1)Orthopaedic-Traumatology Surgery Department, Sibiu Emergency Clinical 
Hospital, 550024 Sibiu, Romania.
(2)Department of Industrial Machinery and Equipments, Lucian Blaga University of 
Sibiu, 550024 Sibiu, Romania.
(3)Department of Surgery, Lucian Blaga University of Sibiu, 550024 Sibiu, 
