Material Behavior and Fatigue Assessment of Old Steel Bridges of the Spanish 
Conventional Rail Network.

Presno Vélez Á(1), Bernardo Sánchez A(2), Bruna OA(3), Abella DM(4), de Prado 
LÁ(2), Fernández MM(2).

Author information:
