Author information:
(1)Trauma Center, Gamma Knife Center, Department of Neurosurgery, Cannizzaro 
Hospital, 95126 Catania, Italy.
(2)Department of Neurosurgery, Highly Specialized Hospital and of National 
Importance "Garibaldi", 95122 Catania, Italy.
(3)Department of Biomedicine and Prevention, University Hospital of Rome "Tor 
Vergata", 00133 Rome, Italy.
(4)Plastic Surgery Unit, Cannizzaro Hospital, 95126 Catania, Italy.
